SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[AuctionStatus], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[IsNotificationSent], [t].[ProductId], [t].[StartTime], [t].[ProductId0], [b].[BidId], [b].[AuctionId], [b].[BidAmount], [b].[BidTime], [b].[UserId], [t].[ApprovalStatus], [t].[Brand], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Condition], [t].[Country], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[Location], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Quantity], [t].[SellerId], [t].[StartingPrice], [t].[Stock], [t].[UnitsSold], [t].[UpdatedAt], [t].[Views]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[AuctionStatus], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [a].[IsNotificationSent], [a].[ProductId], [a].[StartTime], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p].[ApprovalStatus], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Condition], [p].[Country], [p].[CreatedAt], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[Location], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Quantity], [p].[SellerId], [p].[StartingPrice], [p].[Stock], [p].[UnitsSold], [p].[UpdatedAt], [p].[Views]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [a].[AuctionId] = @__auctionId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Bids] AS [b] ON [t].[AuctionId] = [b].[AuctionId]
ORDER BY [t].[AuctionId], [t].[ProductId0]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT TOP(1) [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

2024-11-20 18:01:38.602 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (27ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

2024-11-20 18:05:36.660 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (25ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]

END AS [HighestBidderName]

    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'

) AS [t]

SELECT TOP(1) [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT TOP(1) [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]

    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]

ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT TOP(1) [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]
2024-11-20 19:14:42.481 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (10ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(1) [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT TOP(1) [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[EndTime], [t].[StartTime], [t].[ProductId], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[StartingPrice], [c].[CategoryName]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[EndTime], [a].[ProductId], [a].[StartTime]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE()
    ORDER BY [a].[ProductId]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [t].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[CategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[ProductId]

END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]

    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

FROM (
    SELECT [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[EndTime], [a].[ProductId], [a].[StartTime], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[CategoryId] = @__categoryId_0 AND [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE()

) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[EndTime], [t].[StartTime], [t].[ProductId], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[StartingPrice], [c].[CategoryName]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[EndTime], [a].[ProductId], [a].[StartTime]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE()
    ORDER BY [a].[ProductId]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [t].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[CategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[ProductId]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

2024-11-20 21:19:49.338 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT TOP(1) [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[EndTime], [t].[StartTime], [t].[ProductId], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[StartingPrice], [c].[CategoryName]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[EndTime], [a].[ProductId], [a].[StartTime]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE()
    ORDER BY [a].[ProductId]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [t].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[CategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[ProductId]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

SELECT [t].[AuctionId], [t].[EndTime], [t].[CurrentHighestBid], [t].[ProductName], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[StartingPrice], CASE
    WHEN [u].[UserId] IS NOT NULL THEN [u].[Username]
    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE [p].[ApprovalStatus] = N'Accepted' AND [a].[EndTime] > GETDATE() AND [a].[AuctionStatus] = N'ongoing'
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[CurrentHighestBidderId] = [u].[UserId]
ORDER BY [t].[c]

    ELSE N'No bids yet'
END AS [HighestBidderName]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [a].[AuctionId], [a].[CurrentHighestBid], [a].[CurrentHighestBidderId], [a].[EndTime], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[ProductName], [p].[StartingPrice], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Auctions] AS [a]
